<materialsCitation id="3B1A3CF8935D8E00F2AAFA0EFCDCFA11" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3798147341" collectorName="J. Serrano" pageId="4" pageNumber="488" specimenCount="2" typeStatus="lectotype">
The specimen here designated as 
